locality: relict forest on gentle slopes. Much bamboo in undergroth. Canaopy to 15m with Symphonia , Sloanea etc.
Ambositra: 8 km NNW of Ilaka Afovoany
Amoron'i Mania, Ambatofinandrahana, Itremo, Itremo, forêt d'Antsirakambiaty. Echantillon préservé en alcool. Collecté avec G. Randrianandrasana, Fidele, Rafety & Rababany.
